title: Audio and video accessory for an electronic device

claims.preamble: The ornamental design for an audio and video accessory for an electronic device, as shown and described.

description: FIG. 1 is a perspective view of an audio and video accessory fro an electronic device showing our new design;
FIG. 2 is a front elevational view thereof;
FIG. 3 is a rear elevational view thereof;
FIG. 4 is a right side elevational view thereof;
FIG. 5 is a left side elevational view thereof;
